Math-Rational-Approx

Find rational number approximations to real numbers.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

	perl Makefile.PL
	make
	make test
	make install


DEPENDENCIES

Runtime:

  Moo
  MooX::Types::MooseLike::Numeric

Testing:

  Test::More
  Test::Exception
  Math::Trig


